description._content: Collection: Human Ecology Historical Photographs Title: Caption reads: ''That interest in food conservation is limited neither to sex or age is proven by the 'Victory Special' - a typical daily crowd. There is a group of people, mostly women, gathered in front of the car, and Lucille Brewer of the home economics department staff is standing on the steps in the background. No date given.
